{
  "title": "Home IDS 🛡️ Tier 2: Network & Lateral (Zeek NDR)",
  "uid": "ids-tier2-ndr",
  "tags": ["ids", "tier2", "ndr", "zeek", "showcase"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "refresh": "1m",
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "PROMETHEUS_DS",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "label": "Prometheus Source"
      },
      {
        "name": "LOKI_DS",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "loki",
        "label": "Loki Source"
      },
      {
        "name": "device",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
        "query": "label_values(home_ids_risk_score, hostname)",
        "refresh": 1,
        "includeAll": true,
        "customAllValue": ".*",
        "multi": false,
        "current": { "text": "All", "value": ".*" }
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": { "h": 2, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### 🧭 [Triage Hub](/d/ids-master-hub-ultimate?var-device=${device}) | [📊 DNS & ML Diagnostics](/d/ids-tier2-dns/home-ids-tier-2-dns-ml-diagnostics?var-device=${device}) | **🔒 Network & Lateral (Zeek NDR)** | [🌍 GeoIP & OSINT Intel](/d/ids-tier2-geo/home-ids-tier-2-geoip-osint-intel?var-device=${device}) | [⚙️ Engine System Health](/d/ids-system-health/home-ids-tier-2-engine-system-health)"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "📖 Analyst Field Guide: Catching the Kill Chain",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 2 },
      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### 🚨 Threat: Defense Evasion & Lateral Movement\n**How to hunt:** Zeek monitors physical network flow, catching threats that DNS misses. Charts use 'Step' tracking: if a line jumps up and drops a red point, an event fired.\n* 🔴 **Threat Hunt (Evasion):** DoH Bypass > 0 means malware is encrypting its DNS via Cloudflare to blind your Pi-hole. JA3 Hits > 0 means the device is using a known malware TLS certificate.\n* 🔴 **Threat Hunt (Lateral Scans):** If Lateral Movement hits spike, a device is attacking your own network. Check the **Internal Lateral Matrix** table below to see the exact target IP and port. If S0/REJ states spike, the device is blindly port-scanning."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "DoH Bypass Attempts (Cloudflare, Google, Quad9)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_zeek_doh_bypass{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}}" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 1 } ] }, "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "lineInterpolation": "stepAfter", "showPoints": "always", "pointSize": 5, "fillOpacity": 20 } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Internal Lateral Movement (SSH, RDP, SMB scanning)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_zeek_lateral_moves{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}}" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 1 } ] }, "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "lineInterpolation": "stepAfter", "showPoints": "always", "pointSize": 5, "fillOpacity": 20 } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Suspicious Ext Ports",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_zeek_suspicious_ports{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}}" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 80 } ] }, "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "lineInterpolation": "stepAfter", "showPoints": "always", "pointSize": 5, "fillOpacity": 20 } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "JA3 Malicious TLS Hits",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 6 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_zeek_ja3_malicious{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}}" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 1 } ] }, "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "lineInterpolation": "stepAfter", "showPoints": "always", "pointSize": 5, "fillOpacity": 20 } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "📖 Analyst Field Guide: Target Mapping",
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 14 },
      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### 🎯 Threat: Lateral Matrix & Port Reconnaissance\n* 🔴 **Threat Hunt:** Use this table to map the blast radius of a compromised machine. The 'Target Port' reveals the attacker's goal (Port 22 = Brute-forcing SSH, Port 445 = Spreading ransomware via SMB/Windows file sharing)."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Internal Lateral Movement Forensic Matrix (Src -> Target:Port)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 17 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (hostname, src_ip, dst_ip, dst_port) (increase(home_ids_zeek_lateral_targets_total{hostname=~\"$device\"}[1h])) > 0",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": { "Time": true, "__name__": true },
            "renameByName": {
              "hostname": "Attacking Host",
              "src_ip": "Source IP",
              "dst_ip": "Target Internal IP",
              "dst_port": "Target Port",
              "Value": "Scan / Connection Hits (1h)"
            }
          }
        },
        { "id": "sortBy", "options": { "fields": [ { "desc": true, "displayName": "Scan / Connection Hits (1h)" } ] } }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "custom": { "align": "center" } },
        "overrides": [
          { 
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Scan / Connection Hits (1h)" }, 
            "properties": [ 
              { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "thresholds", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 1 } ] } },
              { "id": "custom.displayMode", "value": "color-background" }
            ] 
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "TCP Port Scan Failures (S0 / REJ Connection States)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 25 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_zeek_s0_rej_count{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}} (S0/REJ)" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "yellow", "value": 15 }, { "color": "red", "value": 50 } ] }, "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "lineInterpolation": "stepAfter", "showPoints": "always", "pointSize": 5, "fillOpacity": 25 } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Max Connection Lifespan (Covert Shell / Tunnel Duration)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 25 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_zeek_max_duration{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}} Duration" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "s", "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "yellow", "value": 14400 }, { "color": "red", "value": 43200 } ] }, "custom": { "fillOpacity": 10, "lineWidth": 2 } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "📖 Analyst Field Guide: Data Exfiltration & C2",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 33 },
      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### 🚨 Threat: Data Exfiltration & C2 Beaconing\n* 🔴 **Threat Hunt (Exfiltration):** A massive spike in 'Outbound Bytes Z-Score' (> 5.0) means an attacker is actively stealing data or dumping a large payload to the internet. \n* 🔴 **Threat Hunt (C2 Beaconing):** Malware 'beacons' a hacker's server periodically. If a bar appears in the Jitter CV chart, Zeek tracked a connection with robotic, mechanical timing precision (< 10% variance). This is a confirmed Command & Control channel."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "TCP/UDP Data Exfiltration Z-Score (Outbound Bytes)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 37 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_outbound_bytes_zscore{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}}" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "orange", "value": 3 }, { "color": "red", "value": 5 } ] }, "custom": { "fillOpacity": 15, "lineWidth": 2 } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Machine C2 Beaconing (Jitter CV < 0.1)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 37 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_beaconing_c2_count{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}}" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 1 } ] }, "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "lineInterpolation": "stepAfter", "showPoints": "always", "pointSize": 5, "fillOpacity": 20 } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Minimum Timing Coefficient of Variation (Jitter)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 37 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_jitter_cv_score{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}} CV Token" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "red", "value": 0 }, { "color": "green", "value": 0.1 } ] }, "custom": { "fillOpacity": 0 } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "logs",
      "title": "🔎 Filtered Workspace: Defense Evasion & Lateral Movements (Loki)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 45 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "${LOKI_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "{job=\"home_ids_alerts\", environment=\"production\"} |~ \"(?i)doh tunneling bypass|internal lateral movement|suspicious destination port|zeek notice|exfiltration payload burst|jitter clock verification|single-domain beaconing|port scan|covert tunnel\" | json | device_hostname=~\"$device\"" } ],
      "options": { "showLabels": false, "wrapLogMessage": true, "enableLogDetails": true }
    }
  ]
}